                   *************   Networking  **************
                   
                   
  ** window me Virtual box se connect hone pr hame IP window provide karata h jisse hm use ping or ssh nhi kr skte to eske liye hme server ko direct router se connect krne k liye VB ki setting -->> Network -->> Bridged Adapter pr set krna padta h.
                     
    Networking is as like as communication between two person
        Requirements to communicate :- Capability, same Language, same Medium
        
        For system requirement
               1. Capability      -->>> NIC card
               2. Medium      ---- (i) Wired
                                   (ii) Wireless  -------- Router, Hub, Switch
               3. Language   ---->>> Protocol       (i) TCP (Transmission Control Protocol)
                                                    (ii) UDP (User Datagram Protocol) 
               
               
          1. Hub   :- esse connected user1 agar kisi ko kuchh send krta h to, wo msg hub se connected sare users dekh or use kr skte hn.
          2. Switch:- eske use se agar koi user kisi ko kuchh send krta h to, wo msg switch se connected whi user dekh sakta h jise wo msg send kiya gaya h, ek switch se connected user kisi dusare switch se connected user se baat nhi kr sakta h.
          3. Router:- esme bhi hm jise msg send krte hn only whi ese dekh or use kr skta h, but router kisi ek router se connected user kisi dusare router se connected user se bhi baat krwa skta h agar wo user capable h to.
          
          
          <<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<------------     IP     ------------->>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
          
          
          1. Private IP     ---->>> ye IP router users ko deta h.
          2. Public IP      ---->>> ye IP ISP router ko di jati h.
          
      Ranges of Private IPs :--
              1.    10.0.0.0 --- 10.255.255.255
              2.    192.168.0.0 --- 192.168.255.255
              3.    172.16.0.0 --- 172.31.255.255
              
              
      *** Subnet/Netmask 
         *Class A --->>> 255.0.0.0       available IPs = 2^24
         *Class B --->>> 255.255.0.0     available IPs = 2^16
         *Class C --->>> 255.255.255.255 available IPs = 2^8
         
         
   ** Kisi dusare system se baat krne k liye only IP ek complete address nhi hota h, because wo to only system tak hi rahta h, or us system k andar bahut sare apps hote hn jisse aapko pta hi nhi chalega ki aap kis app k through baat krna chahte hn.
   
   ** To eske liye IP k sath Port no. use hote hn jiski size 16 bits hoti h, means aap ek IP se only 2^16 apps ek sath chala sakte hn.
   
   ** Sari webs 
          
          
          
          
          
      
