         Dynamic IP:- jab mahara instance running mode me rahta h tab to uske pas uski public IP rahti h, but jab instance stopped rahta h to
                      uske pas koi public IP nhi hoti h. Ese hi dynamic IP bolte hn.
         Elastic IP:- Jab hm apne Instance me Elastic IP allocate kr dete hn to fir chahe hm instance ko running mode me rakhe y fir stopped
                      mode me uski public IP kabhi change nhi hoti h.
                      * Or agr elastic ip ko htana h to use disassociate krn k bad release bhi krn hota h, nhi to tb tk charge lgte rhenge.
                      
       <<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<-----------  Scaling  ---------->>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
       
         Hamara instance 1Gb storg or 1core CPU k h or usme ek web run ho rhi h, ab mana ye 100 users tak ki capecity rakhta h to agr 100 se
         jyada users aa jayenge to website down ho jayegi eske liye hme apne instance ki capecity ko badani padegi. eske do tareeke hn.
         
         
         1. Vertical Scaling:- Es method me hm same instance ki capacity increase krke 2Gb storg or 2core CPU kr dete hn jisse ab 200 users
            aa sakenge, or apni capacity wali problem to solve ho jati h, but ek new problem ye aa jati h ki kisi bhi systm ki manually ram
            change krne k liye use shut down krna hi pdta h, mtlb tab tak koi bhi user web k use kr hi nhi sakta h jisse to jyda loss hoga.
            Eska use movies download krane wali webs me hota h, usme server1, server2,..... hota h.
                                               ___
                            ___               |   |                       ^
                           |   |              |   |                       |
                           |   |   ====>>     |   |   ====>>   200 users  |      {Vertically increased}
                           |___|              |   |                       |
                            1GB               |___|
                                               2GB
       
         2. Horizontal scaling:- Es method me hm esi instance k jaisa ek aur instance le lete hn, dono ki capacity 100-100 users ki h to es 
            tarah bhi totel 200 users website ko use kr skte hn. or hamari users wali problm solv ho jati h, but esme hamare pas do machine 
            hn to unke alag-2 IPs or Domain Names bhi honge jisse user agr pahla domain search krta h or usme traffic bahut hota h to use fir
            se dusara domain search krna padega tab wo web chala payega, man lo abhi to do hi instances hn to do bar hi search krna padta h,
            fir jab or jyada traffic ho jayega to or jyada instances lagenge jisse users ko jyada problems hongi.
            
                            ___         ___                        ^
                           |   |       |   |                       |
                           |   |   +   |   |   ===>>   200 users   |      {Horizontally increased}
                           |___|       |___|                       |
                            1GB         1GB
                          1.1.1.1     1.1.1.2
        
            Es problem ko bhi solve krne k tareeka hamare paas h ===>>> Load Balancer***
            
         *** Load Balancer:-  This is also a type of Instance, which has it's own IP. jab koi user hamari web search krta h to wo LB k pas 
                              pahuchta h, or LB use kam traffic wale instance k pas pahucha deta h, jisme apni website chal rhi h.
         
         
                            ___
                           |   |
                           |Ins|`                                            .
                           |___|    `                                       / \
                            1GB         `                                  /   \
                          1.1.1.1           `                             /     \
                                                `                        /       \
                                                    `     <<<===        /   ELB   \     <<<===  Users
                            ___                 `                      /           \
                           |   |            `                         /             \
                           |Ins|        `                            /_______________\              
                           |___|    `
                            1GB `                       
                          1.1.1.2         
         
         
         Ese elastic load balancer bhi kahte hn, Eske 4 types hote hn.
         
         1. Application LB   {only avalable for http,https (web only)}   Aap http/https k port no. change kr skte hn.
         2. Network LB       {All TCP}  (use for High Traffic Management)
         3. Gateway LB       {All TCP}  (use for block fake IPs)
         4. Classic LB       {All TCP}
         
          Application LB:- 2 instance banane hn or dono me apache2 server se pages run karane hn.
                           es pure ko agr short cut me krna h to Instance banate time hi no. of instances 2 kr dene hn or apache2 server or 
                           pages banane k liye ek scripy likhenge jo ki advance setting me sabse last me likhi jati h,
                           usme es script ko likhna h.
                                #!/bin/bash
                                apt update
                                apt install apache2 -y
                                echo "<h1> Helloooo.... This is inst One </h1>"  >  /var/www/html/index.html
                                
          Agr script change krni h to, Actions ==>> Instance settings ==>> edit user data ||
          
          Ab eske bad hme ek target group create krna h or apne instances ko us group se connect krna h.
          Target group ==>> Create trgt grp ==>> trgt type Instances ==>> grp name ==>> HTTP ==>> IPv4 ==>> HTTP1 ==>> next ==>> select your
                            instances to add in grp ==>> Include as pending below ==>> create trgt grp
                            
          Or ab hme Load balancer create krna h.
          Load balancer ==>> create LB ==>> App LB create ==>> LB name,internate facing,IPv4 ==>> select the availability zones jisme apne
          Instances hn ==>> default & wizard 1 ==>> Listeners and routing me select your target group ==>> create load balancer ||
          
          Bs ab load balancer me jakr DNS name copy krke browser me search krna h or jitni bar refresh karenge utni bar ye page switch karega
          Load balancer page switch krne k liye "Round Robin" Algorithm k use krta h.
          Or ab agr hm ek instance ko band kr dete hn to to fir hm chahe jitni bar refresh karenge hme only ek hi page dikhega.
          
