       <<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<--------- Auto Scaling --------->>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
       
       Auto scaling me basically ky hota h ki agr hamare instance ki capacity 300 traffic ki hi h, or traffic 295 ho chuka h or kabhi 300+
         ho sakta h to 295 traffic me hi automatic ek new instance create ho jaye or agr traffic fir se kam ho kr 290 ho gya or etne me hi 
         continue h to automatic hi new added instance delete ho jaye.
       Hm usko ye bhi bta skte hn ki min ek instance chalne dena or, traffic chahe jitna aa jaye 5 instance se jyada mt create krna, or jaise
         hi auto scaling grp start ho min 2 instance chala dena or check kr lena ki sab kuchh shi h y fir nhi or agr traffic 1 k liye hi h to
         ek instance band kr dena, ese "Desired Capacity" bolte hn.
       To esme hme 3 capacity deni hoti h Min, Max or Desired capacity.
       Or agr hm starting me created dono instances ko terminte kr dete hn to ye fir se ek instance create kr deta h bcs min desired cap is 1
       Instance ko create krne k liye uski storage,CPU,OS,key-pair,etc... ki need hoti h to eske liye hm ek "Template" create krte hn.
       
       Creating a launch template=======----->>>>>>>
         templete name==>> provide guidence checked ==>> Quick start,OS,Instance type,key-pair,security group ==>> Create launch template ||
       
       Creating an Auto scaling group======----->>>>>>>
         group name, select created launch template ==>> next, select zones ==>> next, No load B ==>> next, 2 desired cpcty, min 1, max 3,
         Target tracking scaling, Avrg CPU utilization 50%, no policy, next ,next, next, review ==>> create auto scaling group ||
         
       "stress -c 4" ==>> es cmd se CPU utilization 100% ho jata, ye dekhne k liye hm "top" cmd chalate hn. or increase hote hi new Instance
       create ho jata h. 
 
