         <<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<-----------  Creating a RDS server ---------->>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
         
      first create a data base on MySQL, ab es data base ko connect krne k liye Koi Instance/MySQL client(in window) chahiye.
      "sudo apt install mysql-client-core-8.0" :- cmd to install mysql client. Or ab es mysql client se data base ko connect krna h.
      
      "mysql -h database-2.cfe4i68kyrek.us-east-1.rds.amazonaws.com -u admin -p" :- cmd to connect data base with mysql client.
         -h or -u ke beech me jo likha h wo endpoint hota h jo used data base pr click krte hi mil jata h or -u k bad user name likhna hota h
         
      or agr fir bhi ye data-base ko connect nhi kr rha to syd eske security group ne connect krne k liye allow hi n kiya ho.
      eske liye us database k security group pr click krke ==>> edit inbound rules,add rule,All TCP,Anywhere IPv4 ==>> Save rules ||
      Then run the same command again and enter correct pass and you got connect with the data base.
      
      Commands of MySQL :-    show databases;                         :- To show all databases in your machine.
      			       create database newdatabase;            :- To create a new database named newdatabase
      			       use newdatabase;                        :- To use newdatabase to create data on that
      			       CREATE TABLE table-name;                :- To create a table ]"(id int, name varchar(20), city varcher(20));"]
      			       desc tablename;                         :- To show created table.
      			       ISERT INTO table-name (col1, col2,...); :- To enter column into table.
      			       VALUES (value1, value2,....);           :- To enter value into table.
      			       
      		cmd to create table:-    mysql> create table info (
          			         -> id int,
          			         -> name varchar(20),
          			         -> city varchar(20));
          			         
    Agr hm apne database k backup rakhna chahte hn to hme "Take snapshot" lena padta h jo jyada chargable h to ek aur option h "read replica"
     ese create krte hi basically ek aur database create ho jata h or jo bhi hm apne database me banate hn wo sb replica me bhi bn jata h.
     or replica bhi chargable h.
     
     
