       <<<<<<<<<<<<<-----------  Git & Github (GUI) ----------->>>>>>>>>>>>>>
       
    Github k use apne code ko store krne k liye kiya jata h.
    Git k use stored code ko maintain rakhne me hota h. Esme hm apne sare commits k code ko dekh skte hn.
    
    Fork :- kisi dusre ki repo fork krne pr wo repo hamare repo me aa jati h, or hm usme change krke uske owner k pas hamare kiye gye change
            ko apn repo me add krn k liye ek request send krte hn, jise "Open Pull Request" kahte hn. ye usi edited repo me ja kr Contribute
            section me hota h. or fir ye req owner k pas jayegi wo hamare edited code ko dekhega, agr use accha lagega to wo hamari pull req
            ko "Merge" kr dega or uski repo me hamara code edit ho jayega.
            
            Agr kisi ne line no. 4 me change krke PR send kiya tha or Owner ne PR ko Merge kr diya h or ab fir kisi dusre ne line no.4 me hi
             PR send kr di h to ab Owner us dusri PR ko Merge nhi kr skta h kyoki ek bar us line me change ho chuka h, agr use Merge hi krna
             h to use line no.4 k code delete krna hoga.
            Esk liye Github me bhi "Resolve Conflict" name k ek optn aane lga h. jisme ky hota h ki dono (PR send krne wale) logo k changes
             us code me line by line rahte hn, or fir aap PR Merge kr skte hn.
             
            Or agr aapko Conflict nhi chahiye to aap pahle "Sync Fork" kare fir uske bad PR generate kare to conflict nhi hoga. 
            
            Jaise acchi companies me 1 project me bahut log kam kr rhe hote hn to wo bhi apna code likh kr use github me dal dete hn to sara
             code hme mil jata h or hm check kr lete hn, but esme ek problem h ki esme pta kaise chalega ki kisne ky commit kiya h kyoki ek 
             hi repo me sare kaam kr rhe hn to eske liye github me ek or tareeka h "Branch" name k esme sare devlopers k liye diff branches 
             hoti hn or wo sab apni-2 branch me kaam krte hn.
         
         
