     ab se pass k jagah me token no. dala jata h, ye token no. generate kiye jate hn, or ye unique hote hn koi bhi hamara user name or token
     no. lekr hamari repo me change kr skta h. hm apne token ki permissions ko bhi manage kr skte hn.
     
    Creating token:- Github profile => settings => Developer settings => Personal access tokens => Tokens(Classic) => Generate new Token ||
    
